preference.name: CATIA_update_import_spreadsheet
preference.preference_description: Preserve/Delete the current import spreadsheet when starting a create import spreadsheet process. Possible values: - true: Import spreadsheet is preserved. The existing spreadsheet will be updated. - false: Import spreadsheet is deleted. A new spreadsheet will be created.
